
ikaaro 0.61.2 (2010/04/14)
==========================

This is a Content Management System built on Python & itools, among
other features ikaaro provides:

 - content and document management (index&search, metadata, etc.)
 - multilingual user interfaces and content
 - high level modules: wiki, forum, tracker, etc.

Among many other changes, the wiki includes a new feature that allows
to generate an ODT document from an explicitly defined set of wiki
pages, and using an ODT template.  This makes the wiki a nifty tool to
cooperatively write a document.  This new feature uses the lpod [1]
library to generate the ODT document.

Now the contact form includes a text captcha to avoid spamming.

The bundled TinyMCE [2] has been updated to the 3.3.2 version.


[1] http://lpod-project.org/
[2] http://tinymce.moxiecode.com/


